# FireSim Global Standards

- Tech Stack: Next.js 15 App Router, Bun runtime, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, Shadcn/ui.
- Package Manager: Always use `bun` for installing packages and running scripts. Do not use `npm` or `yarn`.
- Documentation: Rely on Context7 for up-to-date documentation regarding Mastra, Better Auth, Next.js, and Drizzle.
- Proxies: The DEVS-FIRE server uses plain HTTP. Never call it directly from the browser; always proxy through Next.js API routes.
- Types: Enforce strict TypeScript types across all files.